Package: BiocAnnotationLab
Title: An umbrella package organizing information on annotation strategies
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Vince",
           family = "Carey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stvjc@channing.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4046-0063"))
Description: This package organizes information and documentation
	on annotation strategies of use with Bioconductor.
	This provides an open resource as we sunset the 
	AnnotationPipeline and AnnotationDbi strategies that
	have served the community for two decades.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0), tools, utils, methods
